<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.7.12">
<l>tāmō taraṉait taṉimutalvaṉai ñāla muṇṭavaṉai</l>
<l>yāmō taramaṟiya voruvark keṉṟē toḻumavarkaḷ</l>
<l>tāmō taraṉuru vākiya civaṟkun ticaimukaṟku</l>
<l>māmō taramaṟiya vemmāṉai yeṉṉāḻi vaṇṇaṉaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who worship saying “is it possible for anyone to know the greatness(?)</l>
<l>of Tāmotara, the solitary first one, the one who swallowed the world?”,</l>
<l>is it possible even for Śiva and the one with faces in the directions, who are the form</l>
<l>of Tāmotara, to know the greatness(?) of our lord, my ocean-coloured one?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
